{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji8.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致彭德怀电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年1月4日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个月后红军大量扩充，必须现在就准备，抽出老兵入教导营。有了红校就不需要教导营的理由是不对的，红校是训练连长的，教导营是训练排长的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕甘支队和二十五军经过远征的战士，原则上每人都要使之成为干部，不应该使之当作一个兵去消耗掉。这是很重要的一点。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1936,"month":1,"day":4}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":193,"page_end":193},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}